Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:51.88,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}アシタ→ミライ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.76,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}そうだね　時はNonstop
