Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.05,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.97,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}雖然害怕…但還是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:22.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安穩度日 也太無趣了點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:27.19,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:30.90,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.57,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飛奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:36.74,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回憶在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:42.33,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像認識你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.46,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不論是晴天雨天還是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:49.21,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.63,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從過去到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:51.88,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從明天到未來
